# Shared Package

Cross-workspace types, Zod schemas, and utilities shared between frontend and backend.

## Structure

```
packages/shared/src/
  schemas/            ← Zod schemas (user.ts, order.ts, etc.)
  types/              ← Derived TypeScript types (inferred from schemas)
  utils/              ← Pure utility functions (formatters, validators, constants)
  index.ts            ← barrel export
```

## Rules

- Every schema is the single source of truth. Types are derived via `z.infer<>`.
- Zero framework dependencies — no React, no Node-specific APIs.
- Everything must run in both browser and Node environments.
- Export through barrel `index.ts`. External consumers import from `@repo/shared`.
